        "tab_84dVFP": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "what makes us different",
            "content": "<p>We understand that these pieces aren’t just jewellery – they’re symbols of love, commitment, and the moments that matter most. As proud members of the National Association of Jewellers, we hold ourselves to the highest standards of quality and care.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "open_on_mobile": false
          }
        },
        "tab_xwFx4K": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "conflict-free simulated diamonds",
            "content": "<p>Our pieces feature conflict-free simulated diamonds, hand-set stones for a flawless finish. Our Promise stones boast a 2.18 refractive index, MOHS rating of 8.5. To compare: Diamonds have a 2.41 refractive index and MOHS rating of 10, Swarovski Crystals sit at around 1.6 refractive index, MOHS 6-7</p>",
            "page": "",
            "open_on_mobile": false
          }
        },
        "tab_Xp6TKY": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "our precious metals",
            "content": "<p>Our silver pieces are plated in rhodium - one of the world’s most precious metals, known for its mirror-like shine and exceptional resistance to tarnishing.</p><p>Our gold jewellery is crafted using gold vermeil, a technique that requires a thick layer of 18k gold over sterling silver. In fact, our plating is up to 25 times thicker than standard gold-plated jewellery, giving each piece a rich, lasting finish.</p><p>Every design is then sealed with an e-coating, adding an invisible layer of protection to preserve its beauty over time.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "open_on_mobile": false
          }
        }
      },
